Method.袨褌泻褉褘褌褜袧邪胁懈谐邪褑懈芯薪薪褍褞小褋褘谢泻褍.Param.袨锌芯胁械褖械薪懈械.Description=notification about the opening result.\nIf the notification is not specified, a warning will be shown in case of error.\nApplicationStarted - Boolean - True, if the external application did not cause errors when opening.\nAdditionalParameters - Arbitrary - value that was specified when creating the NotifyDescription object.
